---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - shroom-mates">
  <main>
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <div class="content">
      <p>We are passionate about growing high-quality mushrooms in Leipzig. Our mission is to provide the freshest, most flavorful mushrooms while promoting sustainable farming practices.</p>
      
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>Founded by mushroom enthusiasts, shroom-mates began with a simple idea: to bring gourmet mushrooms directly from our farm to your table.</p>
      
      <h2>Our Process</h2>
      <p>We carefully cultivate each variety in controlled environments, ensuring optimal growing conditions and the highest quality produce.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  .content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
